OL,3,CTeachers to get permanent contract
OL,4,Cafter one year
OL,6,FTeachers will be given permanent
OL,7,Fcontracts after one year, under new
OL,8,Fmeasures announced by the education
OL,9,Fminister.
OL,11,FHelen McEntee has put forward a new
OL,12,Fset of policy steps to address teacher
OL,13,Fsupply, which also include assistance
OL,14,Ffor eligible teachers who trained
OL,15,Foutside of Ireland to work within the
OL,16,Fcountry.
OL,18,FCurrently teachers are required to
OL,19,Fcomplete two consecutive contracts
OL,20,Fbefore qualifying for a permanent
OL,21,Fposition.
