OL,3,CTeachers to get permanent contract
OL,4,Cafter one year
OL,6,FUnder the new regulations, teachers
OL,7,Ftaking up their first contract in a
OL,8,Fviable teaching post in September 2025
OL,9,Fwill become eligible for a permanent
OL,10,Fcontract in September 2026, provided
OL,11,Fthe post remains viable.
OL,13,FThis eligibility is contingent upon
OL,14,Fsuccessful reappointment following a
OL,15,Fcompetitive recruitment process.
