OL,4,Cafter one year
OL,6,FTeachers not covered by this new
OL,7,Fpolicy, such as those in substitute
OL,8,Froles or those whose posts are not
OL,9,Fdeemed viable after one year, will
OL,10,Fcontinue to follow the existing route
OL,11,Fto permanency, which typically
OL,12,Finvolves achieving a contract of
OL,13,Findefinite duration (CID) after a
OL,14,Fthird contract.
