OL,3,CTeachers to get permanent contract
OL,4,Cafter one year
OL,6,FMs McEntee has also committed to
OL,7,Fworking with the Teaching Council to
OL,8,Fstreamline the registration process
OL,9,Ffor eligible teachers who qualified
OL,10,Foutside of Ireland, allowing them to
OL,11,Fapply for registration and complete
OL,12,Ftheir induction requirements within
OL,13,Fthe country.
OL,15,FShe said: "There are currently over
OL,16,F78,000 qualified teachers employed in
OL,17,FIreland, more than ever before. For
OL,18,Ftheir sake, I am determined to address
OL,19,Fjob security and make teaching a more
OL,20,Fattractive, sustainable career.
