OL,6,F"Allowing newly qualified teachers who
OL,7,Fare starting in September to gain a
OL,8,Fpermanent contract a year earlier will
OL,9,Fhelp teachers to place their careers
OL,10,Fon a more stable footing much sooner
OL,11,Fthan before.
OL,13,F"This will provide teachers with the
OL,14,Fcertainty that they need, particularly
OL,15,Fwhen applying for mortgages.
