OL,6,F"Enabling eligible teachers who
OL,7,Fqualified outside of Ireland to apply
OL,8,Ffor registration and complete their
OL,9,Finduction here in Ireland is another
OL,10,Fpractical, common-sense measure that
OL,11,Fwill encourage more teachers to work
OL,12,Fand start their careers here in
OL,13,FIreland.
OL,15,F"I am committed to building on today's
OL,16,Fannouncements and introduce further
OL,17,Fmeasures in the coming months to
OL,18,Ffurther address teacher supply.
