OL,6,F"I am absolutely dedicated to ensuring
OL,7,Fa high-quality and well-staffed
OL,8,Feducation system for all students in
OL,9,FIreland."
OL,11,FThe announcements come as the major
OL,12,Fteaching unions ` Into, TUI and Asti `
OL,13,Fhold conferences this week.
OL,15,FInto said the conferences take place
OL,16,Fat a time of growing frustration among
OL,17,Fteachers regarding the resourcing,
OL,18,Fworkload and staffing of the primary
OL,19,Feducation system.
