OL,4,Cafter one year
OL,6,FThe union's general secretary, John
OL,7,FBoyle, said: "Our job is to teach but,
OL,8,Ftoo often, teachers are being pulled
OL,9,Fin every direction."
OL,11,FHe added: "Workload has become
OL,12,Funsustainable, and that's affecting
OL,13,Frecruitment, retention and the
OL,14,Fwellbeing of our members. Unless this
OL,15,Fis taken seriously, industrial action
OL,16,Fis a real possibility."
OL,18,FMr Boyle welcomed the reduced pathway
OL,19,Ffor permanent contracts as "worth a
OL,20,Ftry", but said the move is "not a
OL,21,Fpanacea".
