OL,6,FThe union is calling for a reduction
OL,7,Fin class sizes and guaranteed
OL,8,Fsubstitute cover for all teacher
OL,9,Fabsences.
OL,11,FInto is also demanding action on
OL,12,Fteacher shortages, including a
OL,13,Frestructuring of salary scales,
OL,14,Fgreater career progression
OL,15,Fopportunities and more teacher
OL,16,Ftraining places.
OL,18,FIt also says teachers need stronger
OL,19,Fsupport from psychological,
OL,20,Ftherapeutic and counselling services
OL,21,Fat school level.
