OL,6,FMr Boyle said: "High living costs,
OL,7,Flimited career incentives and lack of
OL,8,Fhousing are driving teachers abroad or
OL,9,Fout of the profession altogether.
OL,11,F"We need serious, targeted
OL,12,Finterventions, not vague commitments."
